text: Æþelmæres booc æt cetwuda & hildes dune twuentig hida on ece yrfe.
Þis seond ða londgemæru ðæs londes æt Cetwuda & æt hildes dune.
Ærest on ða halgan æc.
Swa ollonc ðæs gemær heges to ðæm slo æt ðæm more ufewerdan.
Of ðam more on dunes pyt.
Ðonon ðurh wippan hoh.
Þæt swa be ðæm gretan wyrtruman on ðone holan weg.
On þone oðerne weg to þæm rugan hlawe.
On þone oðerne weg to þæm rugan hlawe.
Up of ðæm sice to cufanlea.
On ða dic to þæm readan slo.
Ðæt swa on þane lytlan dic.
Þonon on ðone oðerne dic.
Þæt swa ollonc þæt gemære heges.
On butan hreodlege þæt swa on þone mærhege þe sceot to þære halgan æc.
Þis lond ælfstan sald æþelfled wiþ þæm.
Lond æt Ceadeles funtan & eft Eadred cing hit ageaf.
Æþelmære wið þæm ilcan land.
A on ece yrfe þæm ðe him leofast seon.
Oda aercabiscop, Oswulfad <bebb>hehgr, Vrm eorl, Vhtred eorl, Wulfhelm biscop.
